text:
Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation. Not only that, but the rest of the world has been taken over by a group of genetically enhanced super-humans called the MAGA. They are led by Rudolph Giuliani III and Donald Trump IV, who snuck out of America during the war and have been hiding in Russia with the Putins.

The only thing now standing in the way of the MAGA's plans to take over the world is the United States. Rudy appears at The Four Seasons and can be seen explaining why MAGA is good each night on Fox.

The MAGA are able to control the minds of the American people by using a device called the "MAGA-tron" to broadcast. These broadcasts come to every viewer of Fox news. The MAGA-tron is powered by the "MAGA-tron core" which is a small, glowing orb that is kept in a can that reads Diet Coke.

The MAGA-tron broadcasts are very effective and have turned the Fox viewers into mindless drones. When election day comes, they all check a box next to "Vladamir et al" and go back to watching Fox. The election returns show 10,000,000 MAGA votes and 70,000,000 votes for the Democrats. "MAGA Landslide" scream the banners at the bottom of Fox TV.

The MAGA-tron broadcasts are also used to keep the MAGA in line. Red white and blue "Putin" signs flutter from the back of pickup trucks. The MAGA-tron broadcasts tell the MAGA to "get in the truck" and they do. 

The MAGA-tron broadcasts tell the MAGA to "get out of the truck" and they do.

The MAGA-tron broadcasts tell the MAGA to "get under the truck" and they do.

The MAGA-tron broadcasts tell the MAGA to "get on top of the truck" and they do.

"Ain't democracy wonderful?" they ask each other as they climb.
